irc;me sens, qu\'elles apparaissent au singulier ou au pluriel.</span></p>\n<p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><br /></strong></p>\n<p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Arial; color: #944716; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">D&eacute;finitions</span></p>\n<p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><br /></strong></p>\n<p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Aux fins de la pr&eacute;sente politique de confidentialit&eacute; :</span></p>\n<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\n<li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -0.5669291338582667pt;" dir="ltr">\n<p style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&ldquo;Application&rdquo; d&eacute;signe le programme logiciel fourni par la Soci&eacute;t&eacute;, t&eacute;l&eacute;charg&eacute; par vous sur tout appareil &eacute;lectronique, </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none;